Class MemoryRobot

  • Object
    • MemoryRobot
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Robot
    public class MemoryRobot
extends Object
implements Robot
    Class: MemoryRobot Creates a robot which keeps track of the road it has walked. If it can't find a position it hasn't already been in it will go back to where it started and remove that path as a viable option.
